458. Gan. 1978 Apr;69(2):167-77.

Late effects of fetal mice x-irradiated at middle or late intrauterine stage.

Sasaki S, Kasuga T, Sato F, Kawashima N.

Mice of F1 hybrids of (C57BL/6xWHT) strains were exposed in utero to 200 R of 
X-rays at 12 or 16 approximately 18 days post coitum. Mice of both sexes were 
allowed to liver through their life span, and the induction of tumors, growth 
